```
<html>                <!--告诉浏览器HTML从这里开始-->
 <head>               <!--页面head开始-->
  <title>Head First Lounge</title>     <!--为页面指定一个标题-->
 </head>              <!--head结束-->
 <body>               <!--页面主体开始-->
   <h1>Welcome to the Head First Lounge</h1>  <!--告诉浏览器“Welcome to...”是一个标题-->
   <img src="drinks.gif">     <!--在这里放置图像“drinks”-->
   <p>                <!--开始一个段落-->
      Join us any evening for refreshing elixirs,
      conversation and maybe a game or
      two of <em>Dance Dance Revolution</em>. <!--强调DanceDanceRevolution-->
      Wireless access is always provided;
      BYOWS (Bring your own Web server).
   </p>               <!--段落结束-->
   <h2>Directions</h2><!--告诉浏览器“Directions”是个子标题-->
   <p>                <!--开始另一个段落-->
      You'll find us right in the center of downtown Webville. Come join us!
   </p>               <!--段落结束-->
 </body>              <!--页面主体结束-->
</html>               <!--告诉浏览器HTML在这里结束-->
```
